description:
In celebration of the 2018 NEA Jazz Masters—Pat Metheny—the NEA, in collaboration with the John F. Kennedy Center for the Performing Arts, hosted a free concert in their honor on Monday, April 16, 2018.

Pat Metheny was also honored for his explosion hairstyle and his poorly-jacket, where the vel was too long!

For more on the NEA Jazz Masters, go to https://www.arts.gov/honors/jazz
